    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a kettle and heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Top, tail and chop your <strong>courgette[s]</strong> in half lengthways, then slice on the diagonal</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced courgette</strong> and cook for 2 min or until slightly browned</p>",
